'''花蓮清真寺'''，是一座位於台灣[[花蓮縣|花蓮縣]][[花蓮市|花蓮市]]的[[遜尼派|遜尼派伊斯蘭教]]清真寺，也是台灣第9座、花蓮縣第1座清真寺<ref>{{cite news|first1=David|last1=Spencer|date=2018-08-18|url=https://www.taiwannews.com.tw/en/news/3508132|title=Top 6 reasons for Muslim travelers to visit Taiwan|publisher=Taiwan News|access-date=2019-10-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191022015538/https://www.taiwannews.com.tw/en/news/3508132|archive-date=2019-10-22|language=en}}</ref>，於2018年3月18日由印尼前{{Link-en|法律與人權部|Ministry of Law and Human Rights (Indonesia)}}部長{{Link-en|穆罕默德·馬哈福|Mahfud MD}}主持落成儀式。<ref>{{cite news|date=2018-03-22|url=https://www.nu.or.id/post/read/87574/silaturahim-ke-pcinu-taiwan-mahfud-md-sampaikan-pesan-kebangsaan|title=Silaturahim ke PCINU Taiwan, Mahfud MD Sampaikan Pesan Kebangsaan|publisher=NU Online|access-date=2019-10-22|language=id|trans-title=Visited PCINU Taiwan, Mahfud MD Conveyed Nationalism Message|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191010062959/https://www.nu.or.id/post/read/87574/silaturahim-ke-pcinu-taiwan-mahfud-md-sampaikan-pesan-kebangsaan|archive-date=2019-10-10}}</ref>2019年11月10日，花蓮清真寺在大廳設置資訊站與申訴處，服務當地的印尼在台移工。<ref>{{cite news|first1=Gilar|last1=Ramdhani|date=2019-11-19|url=https://www.liputan6.com/news/read/4114125/kdei-taipei-dan-bnp2tki-hadirkan-pos-layanan-informasi-dan-pengaduan-pmi-di-hualien#|title=KDEI Taipei dan BNP2TKI Hadirkan Pos Layanan Informasi dan Pengaduan PMI di Hualien|publisher=Liputan 6|accessdate=2020-05-21|language=id|trans-title=KDEI Taipei and BNP2TKI Present Information and Complaint Service Counter for Indonesian Migrant Workers in Hualien|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200720060525/https://www.liputan6.com/news/read/4114125/kdei-taipei-dan-bnp2tki-hadirkan-pos-layanan-informasi-dan-pengaduan-pmi-di-hualien|archive-date=2020-07-20}}</ref>

